TITLE: Never Gymless: An Excuse-free System for Total Fitness
AUTHOR: Ross Enamait
YEAR: 2006
LANGUAGE: English
FORMAT: PDF

SYNOPSIS: Never Gymless is dedicated to home-based workouts which negate the need for a fully equipped gym. This book promises to be the most comprehensive bodyweight exercise manual on the market. Learn about bodyweight exercise for strength, endurance, and speed. All aspects of athletic training are covered with little or no equipment.
